profile: Shines Energy is the largest Lennox HVAC dealer East of Montreal.   We are partners with Costco and do all of the Nova Scotia Costco's heat pump, gas furnace and HRV installations.  With a great team of Installers, service technicians, sales and support staff your experience with Shines Energy will be a good one.  Your success with the heat pumps you live with is our success as a company.
